snippet.title: End of the Line [SFM]
snippet.description:
Wishlist my new project!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2271050/RESISTOR/

Is it the End of the Line for the RED team?

Team Fortress 2 Update - http://www.teamfortress.com/endoftheline/
Credits - http://www.teamfortress.com/endoftheline/credits/

Please support the artists and musicians!
Poster - https://valvestore.forfansbyfans.com/end-of-the-line-movie-8720.html
Shirt - https://valvestore.forfansbyfans.com/end-of-the-line-movie-8719.html
Music - https://open.spotify.com/album/7jCiXnlNZno4bZNSYNAvyw

Thanks so much to those involved in the project and to all who have supported us during this long ride.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/VioletMcVinnie
